[SHORT DESC]
10% chance to confuse.

[LONG DESC]
<p>Has a 10% chance to confuse the target.
</p>
<h2>Related Moves</h2>
<p><a href="/rs/moves/aurora_beam">Aurora Beam</a> is an Ice-type equivalent, but has a chance to lower the target's Attack instead of confusing it.<br/ >
<a href="/rs/moves/bubblebeam">BubbleBeam</a> is a Water-type equivalent, but has a chance to lower the target's Speed instead of confusing it.<br/ >
<a href="/rs/moves/sludge">Sludge</a> is a Poison-type equivalent, though physical, but has a chance to poison the target instead of confusing it.</p>